{"tid":1199620,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"越南簽證問題","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:47:57.000Z","uid":41417,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a82de8e337c8827d59c601cba552cba8fdd1692b","tid":1199620,"uid":41417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"月尾會去越南玩<br />\n<br />\n網上見特區護照要拎visa ，有兩種，有種係去領事館搞，另一種係E-Visa。<br />\n<br />\n我見有好多網都有得辦e-visa，唔太似官方，之後落機好似仲有手續。<br />\n<br />\n想問下有無人申請過越南e-visa, 詳情係點？"},{"pid":"bb2552e3957492aaa8c0399987f6e50acf54daca","tid":1199620,"uid":68806,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"我個時係喱個網整<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cheapvietnamvisa.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cheapvietnamvisa.net%2F&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=b068beac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cheapvietnamvisa.net/</a><br />\n係佢個網到申請<br />\n最平個隻就得(如果要私隱就貴小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n申請完俾完錢<br />\n佢就會send個email俾你<br />\n有你d資料<br />\n你再send返個email俾佢話俾左錢d料冇錯<br />\n等一兩日佢就會再有email俾個e-visa你<br />\n你要印個visa同一張form出黎<br />\n入境個時帶visa,填好嘅form,錢同埋兩張相去做落地簽就得<br />\noverall平過係香港做簽證<br />\n其實個個正式黎講好似唔係叫e-visa<br />\n只係一個批准信<br />\n但最新好似係有e-visa 應該有唔同<br />\n其實你上網search就有好多教學有埋圖"},{"pid":"cad72b981e6f24cdca386a98d18e2db2a08e7a87","tid":1199620,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"其實仲有種喺arrival visa<br />\n要出發前去agent畀錢申請approval letter<br />\n<br />\n不過揸CNO就e－visa啦<br />\ne－visa得一個網可以搞25美金<br />\napproval letter一般under10美金 去到另外畀USD25"},{"pid":"ff5af3fae0a1bfe47386dbd45000384491c22070","tid":1199620,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"一定evisa 直接搞掂，去到直接過關"},{"pid":"5365e03f5414b70fd3c7388f1faecbdef6f0305d","tid":1199620,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82de8e337c8827d59c601cba5